Yeah, I understand that, Danny.

169
00:09:34,491 --> 00:09:35,742
But I feel like
I got a duty to go.

170
00:09:35,826 --> 00:09:37,828
Don't preach to me
about duty, damn it.

171
00:09:37,953 --> 00:09:39,746
