we understand
both more and less.

2412
02:50:18,056 --> 02:50:20,183
This much is certain.

2413
02:50:20,309 --> 02:50:21,852
Before the Doolittle raid...

2414
02:50:21,894 --> 02:50:24,313
America knew nothing
but defeat.

2415
